# WeatherWhisperÂ ğŸŒ¦ï¸

**WeatherWhisper** is a lightningâ€‘fast, crossâ€‘platform commandâ€‘line interface (CLI) that delivers realâ€‘time weather conditions and fiveâ€‘day forecasts without ever opening a browser. It relies on the free **OpenWeatherMap** API, caches results locally to respect rateâ€‘limits, and supports both metric and imperial units.

